sequenceDiagram
  %% Basis: official architecture page. Adapter-specific behavior pending source verification.
  participant Platform as Messaging Platform
  participant Adapter as Platform Adapter
  participant Gateway as GatewayRunner
  participant Session as SessionStore
  participant Agent as AIAgent
  participant Delivery as Delivery

  Platform->>Adapter: Incoming message
  Adapter->>Gateway: MessageEvent
  Gateway->>Gateway: authorize user
  Gateway->>Session: resolve session key and history
  Gateway->>Agent: create agent with session history
  Agent-->>Gateway: response
  Gateway->>Session: persist update
  Gateway->>Delivery: deliver response
  Delivery->>Platform: outbound message

